#: ../../source/ent_auth.rst:364
msgid "Optionally provide security settings in the **SAML Security Config** field. This field is the equivalent to the ``SOCIAL_AUTH_SAML_SECURITY_CONFIG`` field in the API. Refer to the `OneLogin's SAML Python Toolkit`_ for further detail."
